Package io.cyborgcode.roa.framework.quest

Class SuperQuest

java.lang.Object
io.cyborgcode.roa.framework.quest.Quest
io.cyborgcode.roa.framework.quest.SuperQuest
public final class SuperQuest extends Quest
Provides an enhanced test execution context by delegating core operations to an underlying Quest instance.

The SuperQuest class wraps a Quest instance, delegating methods such as registering or removing test services, retrieving artifacts, accessing storage, and managing soft assertions. This ensures that all functionality available in Quest is seamlessly accessible, while also enabling extended behaviors in the test execution flow.

Methods in this class mirror those in Quest and provide consistent documentation for interacting with the test execution context.
